  What's intentionally NOT shipped (add later if you want)

  - p10k not pre-configured -- first interactive zsh launch will run p10k configure (2 min of prompts).
  - xfce4-panel keeps its default look -- custom panel XML or polybar is future polish.
  - No animated wallpapers -- anime loops need xwinwrap + mpv, deferred.

